{"comments":"ButtonSemantics - semantic purpose taxonomy for button elements.\n\nDistinguishes WHAT a button DOES (purpose) from HOW it LOOKS (variant).\nA PlayButton and a CTAButton have different semantic roles, accessibility\nrequirements, and interaction patterns — regardless of visual styling.\n\n## Why This Matters\n\nAt billion-agent scale, agents must reason about button PURPOSE:\n- \"Find the play button\" vs \"Find the submit button\"\n- \"All media controls should have consistent behavior\"\n- \"Danger actions require confirmation patterns\"\n\nVisual styling (Primary/Secondary/Ghost) is orthogonal to semantic purpose.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[151,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/ButtonSemantics.purs","start":[151,3]},"title":"ActionButton"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[152,15],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/ButtonSemantics.purs","start":[152,3]},"title":"FormSubmit"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[153,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/ButtonSemantics.purs","start":[153,3]},"title":"FormReset"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[154,21],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/ButtonSemantics.purs","start":[154,3]},"title":"NavigationButton"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[155,17],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/ButtonSemantics.purs","start":[155,3]},"title":"MediaControl"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[156,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Reactive/ButtonSemantics.purs","start":[156,3]},"title":"ToggleControl"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declT